title: Grateful Dead Live at The Mecca on 1989-04-16
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket, They Love Each Other, Little Red Rooster, Stagger Lee, Mama Tried-> Mexicali Blues, Bird Song

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain-> Scarlet Begonias-> Saint Of Circumstance-> Truckin'-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Stella Blue-> Throwing Stones-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: Box Of Rain
